a2155b7c7ba308b81120d97b4b912313a6ec75b00849015665bc4104b24ca181bdaacbf65eb12b7527851a4147cbc823f420f6daae3f02f972a6f4125a4e0721  0001-Use-busybox-v1.27.2-install-mode.patch"
